      "id": "PopularPost68806",
      "post_content": "Outstanding little artifact that keeps getting bigger and can dish significant amounts of damage in the right deck.\n  \n   \nThere are tons of ways to get this out for less than it's stated cost. The most obvious one is still Type 2 legal, the [Master Transmuter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Master Transmuter). It is also and Eldrazzi artifact, so there are about 100 new cards that create the spawn you will need to get this thing out early.\n  \n   \nThe final mechanic that makes this thing devastating is Rebound... every time you cast an instant or sorcery with this mechanic, you're getting a 2-for-1 with this item. Toss a [Staggershock](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Staggershock) at an opponet with the wand on the table, and you're hitting for 7 points of damage; not bad for a 3CC instant.\n  \n   \nIt IS expensive, but I am glad it isn't any cheaper or it could be ridiculous.\n  \n   \n4/5\n  ",
      "posted_by": "Gaussgoat",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost68806\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Outstanding little artifact that keeps getting bigger and can dish significant amounts of damage in the right deck.\r<br/> <br/>There are tons of ways to get this out for less than it's stated cost.  The most obvious one is still Type 2 legal, the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Master Transmuter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Master Transmuter\">Master Transmuter</a>.  It is also and Eldrazzi artifact, so there are about 100 new cards that create the spawn you will need to get this thing out early.\r<br/> <br/>The final mechanic that makes this thing devastating is Rebound... every time you cast an instant or sorcery with this mechanic, you're getting a 2-for-1 with this item.  Toss a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Staggershock\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Staggershock\">Staggershock</a> at an opponet with the wand on the table, and you're hitting for 7 points of damage; not bad for a 3CC instant.\r<br/> <br/>It IS expensive, but I am glad it isn't any cheaper or it could be ridiculous.\r<br/> <br/>4/5\r<br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '68806'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy23116\">Gaussgoat</s